{
  "stem": "10549.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that headquarters, there was a lot of other profession, like-- not profession, I mean, carpenters, mechanics, car mechanics, and shoemakers, tailors, and so, so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there was over 140 people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who were servicing that headquarters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that-- after that, I met somebody over there who was from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And instead of being a block laborer, he took me to help him to be a painter, to paint.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I become a painter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I learn how to paint, and I become a painter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I had a little-- it was not so hard for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was much, much easier work by being a painter than carrying coal from the cellar to the fourth or fifth floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe because I worked for them and was a useful Jew-- that's what they used to call it-- so maybe my fate was-- look, look a little bit [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- fortunately later on when they liquidated the ghetto, I was fortunate to save my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But coming back to the situation when working for the headquarters-- when I become a painter, my job was painting [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] walls, officers' halls, whatever, in that, in that headquarters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That headquarters was like three blocks, two blocks square.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a lot of work to do there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And part of my job was painting the walls after they beat up a lot of [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] people, which they were-- not-- interrogating in the Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to beat those poor people to, to, to the-- sometimes to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the blood used to splatter on the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they used to call me to paint over the, the walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now that was part of my job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I see a lot of tragedy at that headquarters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Now [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we used to go, go from the ghetto, used to walk every morning to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to work from 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to be there at 7:00 in the morning until 6:00, 7:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we walk back home every, every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that, that lasted for almost a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once, before we were going home, they told us to meet, that, that we should assemble in one hall, all of the workers that-- they told us to assemble in a hall.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Once we came in-- the Gestapo headquarters had a gate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And once you were in, you could not get out, if you were not allowed to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they assembled us in the headquarters, I mean, in the, in the, in the hall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they gave us the news that we not going back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All 140 people are-- and some people had wives and children living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us that we not going back home anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What, what's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are they-- and we thought, are they going to maybe shoot us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they didn't shoot us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They locked-- they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] packed us on trucks, and they drove us to prison.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gestapo was in charge of all the prisons in, in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a famous prison in, in Cracow named Montelupich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a very old prison, and very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like with dungeons and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very bad prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they locked us up in that prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told us that we not going to go anymore back home to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they will house us in that prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every morning, they load us on the trucks, and we were going to the headquarters to do the work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at night, they brought us back to prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can imagine that it was a very dramatic thing, because I was single.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But between us, between those 140 people, there was a lot of people what they had families, wives, kids, children, in the, in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they were not allowed to see the children or their wives back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we didn't know what's going to happen, but the rumors were that we-- that they're going to liquidate the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because I knew a lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Gestapo officers over there, I plead with one captain [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that my father is a watchmaker, and he's a jeweler, and maybe he will be able to be useful for the, for the headquarters to fix people's watches or-- because they needed people to work.",
      "word_count": 59
    }
  ],
